Hello!

An update on the status of this Journal-

This journal is no longer used for posting purposes, but for keeping track of LJ communities that I'm interested in.

The Greatest Journal that I have been linking to likely does not work due to Greatest Journal going under.

I currently don't have any public journals to link to here.

Also, I just changed the journal layout due to photo bucket issues.
Moved personal journal over to Greatest Journal. This journal remains to be used to keep track of LJ Coms and other things. You can find this new journal over HERE.
